    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 European sports sedan that perfectly balances luxury with daily utility. The exterior is finished in a deep Metallic Charcoal that retains a high-gloss shine, though close inspection reveals minor road peppering on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of black leather and brushed aluminum. The upholstery is free of tears or heavy stains, with only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster from regular use. All cabin technology, including the dual-zone climate control, sunroof, and 10-speaker premium audio system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the turbocharged engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises. This vehicle has a documented service history, including a recent synthetic oil change and a new set of all-season tires installed less than 3,000 miles ago. The brakes are firm, the steering is precise, and the transmission shifts through all gears seamlessly. This is a solid, reliable vehicle that has been cared for with pride and is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 29800.0,
